H0.text: Who produces the `Agila' car model. Opel

H1.text: Who produces the `Agila' car model. Suzuki

H2.text: Who produces the `Agila' car model. Fiat

H3.text: Who produces the `Agila' car model. VAUXHALL

A4.text: The Agila was built at Opel's factory in Gliwice, Poland.

A5.text: European production of the Opel Agila and Suzuki Splash took place at the Magyar Suzuki plant in Esztergom, Hungary.
